title: Counter Strike 1.6 Real Battle + bots. win: XP/7/8/8.1
description:
***********************
* Counter Strike 1.6  *
***********************


Features:

* New Models, New Sounds, New Weapons.
* Fully working serverbrowser with MasterServer
* Latest release of the game, V43, Build 4554.
* Dual Protocol (48 + 47) Client
* Added option to launch listen server in LAN mode
* Included Bots in this release
* Half-Life maps are totally removed
* Windows XP/Vista/7/8/8.1 support
* Ads are removed
* Antislowhack tool included
* Download and Play
